  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/transportation/\" rel=\"tag\">交通相关</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"BMW i8 to use smartphonestyle hardened glass for noise and weight reduction\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/www.engadget.com/media/2013/08/bmw-i8-back-camouflage.jpg\" /></div>\n \n\n<div><br />\n在数码消费领域，现在会经常见到智能手机或者平板电脑采用坚固的钢化玻璃（比如 Gorilla Glass），这样可以让屏幕很耐刮，也能保护内部芯片。BMW 则打算在 i8 上也采用类似的玻璃材质，这也是世界上首款采用这类化学钢化玻璃的量产车型。<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/BMW/\">BMW</a> 将无需采用厚厚的传统汽车夹层玻璃，新材料同样是夹层结构，两个 0.7mm 厚层中间夹着一个隔音片，它能够减轻一半的重量并产生较低的噪音。当然我们要等到 2014 年等到 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/BMWi8/\">BMW i8</a> 开卖之后才能体验到效果，但这应该是未来更轻更安静汽车制造工艺的一种趋势。<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/08/07/bmw-i8-to-use-smartphone-style-hardened-glass/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"https://www.press.bmwgroup.com/pressclub/p/pcgl/pressDetail.html?title=the-bmw-i8-selected-chapters&amp;outputChannelId=6&amp;id=T0144439EN&amp;left_menu_item=node__6729#\" target=\"_blank\">BMW</a>、<a href=\"http://www.autoweek.com/article/20130806/CARREVIEWS/130809888\" target=\"_blank\">Autoweek</a> <a href=\"http://www.autoevolution.com/bmw-blog/bmw-s-i8-will-be-the-first-car-in-the-world-to-use-gorilla-glass-64587.html\" target=\"_blank\">Autoevolution</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n </div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/08/bmw-i8-to-use-smartphone-style-hardened-glass/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20689830/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/08/bmw-i8-to-use-smartphone-style-hardened-glass/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
